channel.title: Developing Team Omega
channel.description:
Development Team: Myself - Lives in The United States Michael - Lives in London
We can host up to 2 servers at a time, first come, first serve.
We have a unique Developing Team because we each live in a different time zone. This means, one of us will most likely be coding.
In 2010, we were coding about 3 different servers at one time, and 2 of which became very successful, which cannot be mentioned due to an aggreement.
If You have MSN and would like our help, PM me and send me your EMAIL. You can then meet Michael and I.
My MSN is Tmonkeynuts@hotmail.com
